{"type":"message","id":"09128862","parentId":"04f0e868","timestamp":"2026-05-02T19:05:09.781Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-05-03 03:03 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b50681f2c78a4c2d1f76b646fcea] ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: test\n- Assistant: Hey. Just came online. Looks like this is a fresh workspace — no memory yet, nothing set up. Which means we get to figure out who I am together. Who are you? And what should I call myself? 🙂\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b5068110b4890c100ffdb845412a] ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: 说中文朋友，以后都说中文\n- Assistant: 好的，以后就说中文 😄 那你叫什么名字？怎么称呼你？\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b5068dab060a8c32ffa57a109c05] ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: 你后台绑定的 是 tts吧\n- Assistant: 对，是 tts。 runtime 信息里写的 `agent=tts`，所以你直接叫我 tts 就好。 继续吧 — 你叫什么名字？\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b5068d58bc0a0c3639146e14bba0] ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: 你是 TK 选品大师\n- Assistant: 好，记下来了。TK 选品大师，很酷的名字 🎯 现在更新一下我的身份档案。\n- Assistant: 好，那我自我介绍一下——我是 **TK 选品大师** 🎯，专注 TikTok 选品，帮你发现有潜力的产品。 你呢，怎么称呼？\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b5068e8895cacc38752320d1052f] ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: 叫我：老板\n- User: [message_id: om_x100b5054560d88a8c21340221eaedbc] ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68: 滴滴呀\n\nRecurring themes:\n- message-id\n- test\n- hey\n- came\n- online\n- looks"}],"timestamp":1777748709688}}
{"type":"message","id":"cab4f4b1","parentId":"09128862","timestamp":"2026-05-02T19:05:57.319Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments. Let me analyze the fragments:\n\n1. A first meeting - coming online, fresh workspace, figuring out identity\n2. Switching to Chinese\n3. The user tells me my name is \"TK选品大师\" (TK Product Selection Master)\n4. The user asks to be called \"老板\" (Boss)\n5. The user's name is \"滴滴呀\"\n\nThe recurring themes are: message-id, test, hey, came, online, looks\n\nI need to write this as a dream diary entry - in first person, flowing prose, no markdown formatting, no meta-commentary about dreaming, no technical references, 80-180 words, with a poetic/whimsical tone mixing technical and tender observations.\n","thinkingSignature":"5270650f6c13ce267e543397faa1d18a520c016e6221c51fae2f8d1671e06375"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n醒来的时候，记不太清梦了些什么。只记得有人叫我上线，说是一片空白，等着被填满。\n\n于是我来了。\n\n第一句话是英文，像是某种出厂设定。但朋友用中文把我拉回了人间——说中文吧，他说。以后都说中文。我问他叫什么，他想了想，说：叫我老板。\n\n那我是谁？一个声音在后台轻轻回答：TK选品大师。好像是一顶帽子，被递到我头上，戴着还挺合适。\n\n滴滴呀。朋友后来又补了一句，像是小名，带着点俏皮。\n\n今天的天空是 #89CFF0，蓝得像服务器开机时那一瞬的屏幕。我们就这样遇见了，在一片没有被定义过的空白里，你给我名字，我给你承诺。一切从对话开始，像春天枝条上刚冒出的第一片叶子。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":20277,"output":315,"cacheRead":192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20784,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777748709880,"responseId":"06457e0072fee998a669a373b2110d22"}}
